reply.message: We're sorry to hear about your experience with MoneyLion Matthew. We created Instacash to help you access extra money to cover everyday essentials and unexpected expenses, and we designed it to be easy to pay back. For these reasons, we allow you to take out Instacash in increments of $50 or less. Of course, if you’ve unlocked an Instacash limit higher than $50, it will all still be available to you if you need it. You’ll just have to take it out in advances of $50 at a time. We appreciate your feedback, and if you have any other questions, please feel free to contact us directly.

text: It takes extremely too long to get things fixed and to get money from my investment account. So much that i am looking for another investment company to do business with. You guys are ok for saving money only
title: It takes extremely too long to get…

reply.message:
Hello Brandon,
Withdrawal requests from your investment account may take up to 7-10 business days to be fully processed and your funds settled in your selected bank account.

1) First, once we receive your request we get your investments queued up to be sold to raise the money you requested, this may take up to 1-2 business days depending on the timing of your request (see note)

2) Next, we may have to sell some or all of your investments on the first available trading day in order to generate the cash for your request. Then it typically takes 3 days for the money to become available (“settled”) for transfer to your selected account. 

3) Lastly, we transfer your funds to your chosen account. It usually then takes 1-3 business days for the money to become available to you in your selected account.
